QorIQ Yocto SDK Project
=======================
QorIQ Yocto SDK is a complete Linux kit for NXP QorIQ SoC's and
the reference and evaluation boards.

Supported boards
================
lx2160ahpcsom

Setting up to use the Yocto project
===================================

(1) Install the 'repo' tool:
$ mkdir ~/bin
$ curl https://storage.googleapis.com/git-repo-downloads/repo > ~/bin/repo
$ chmod a+x ~/bin/repo

(2) Download the metadata:
$ export PATH=${PATH}:~/bin
$ mkdir yocto-sdk
$ cd yocto-sdk
$ repo init -u https://source.codeaurora.org/external/qoriq/qoriq-components/yocto-sdk -b refs/tags/lx2160ahpcsom-bsp0.2
$ repo sync --force-sync

(3) Build images:
$ . ./setup-env -m lx2160ahpcsom
$ bitbake qoriq-composite-firmware
